#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Coords" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
The Coords field contains the latitude and longitude of where to park to deliver to this
patron.  If left blank, this information will be calculated from the address supplied
for the patron.
<p>
This information will be in the form:
<div class=field_format>nnn.nnnnnn,nnn.nnnnnn

